meta-beta
=========

Yocto BSP and application layer for the Beta Humanoid Robot project.
Targets Raspberry Pi with a dual A/B RAUC OTA update layout (scarthgap / Yocto 5.0 LTS).

Dependencies
============

The image currently builds with the following repositories and branches
according to the active build/conf/bblayers.conf.

  1. poky
  -------
  Repository: https://git.yoctoproject.org/poky
  Branch:     scarthgap
  Clone:      git clone -b scarthgap git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky
  Layers used from this repo:
    - meta
    - meta-poky
    - meta-yocto-bsp

  2. meta-beta
  ------------
  Repository: https://github.com/BETA-KNH/meta-beta
  Branch:     main
  Clone:      git clone -b main https://github.com/BETA-KNH/meta-beta.git
  Layers used from this repo:
    - meta-beta

  3. meta-raspberrypi
  -------------------
